## This file contains SV mutations from the matched tumour biopsy for alt-seq mode.
## REF alleles are real nucleotide sequences (not N) because multiseqex --alt-seq
## needs the actual REF bases to substitute the ALT junction sequence.
## IDs are "." so that multiseqex generates clean "chr:start-end" FASTA headers.
